{"tid":31044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好忘記，星期日係投票日！","createTime":"2016-12-09T12:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T11:31:18.000Z","uid":50329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ff2dbfc789f60382f22efb1499fe09ed420d9de","tid":31044,"uid":50329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:27:25.000Z","msg":"雖則星期日係小圈子選舉<br />\n但係今年泛民同傘後組織用咗好大氣力參選<br />\n目標係 300+<br />\n而家 fb 一片喜慶<br />\n但我鄭重呼籲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">星期日有票既人<br />\n絕對唔可以放過手上一票</span><br />\n<br />\n689 呢個人講嘢唔可信<br />\n嚴格嚟講選前兩日做咁大動作<br />\n其實有影響選舉嫌疑<br />\n你試諗下如果後日係立法會大選<br />\n就知問題可以幾嚴重<br />\n<br />\n而家無人知佢下星期會唔會反口<br />\n總之一日 689 未落台<br />\n佢既手段好值得全香港人警惕<br />\n<br />\n為免蘇州選後冇艇搭<br />\n我再講多次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">星期日有票既人<br />\n絕對唔可以放過手上一票</span>"},{"pid":"be6d7b4c324121d5455911adc17d3bc038e58a60","tid":31044,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:31:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1154fdebcc77605316dd74da356f8e7d9778f2a2","tid":31044,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:32:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1353d0c2542a0eaa15aec209a8bfea517a4115df","tid":31044,"uid":50329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:48:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>投咩票?講緊咩?</blockquote><br />\n就係用嚟組成出年三月選特首嗰千二人<br />\n既選舉委會會"},{"pid":"373743de9d48bffa7bbf7f35e72d7aab837aa948","tid":31044,"uid":50329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:49:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>投咩票?講緊咩?</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.elections.gov.hk/ecss2016/chi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Fecss2016%2Fchi%2F&d=J%2FLuuDr6zUwFy%2B1TchZ5TgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=b5a7e11a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.elections.gov.hk/ecss2016/chi/</a>"},{"pid":"49851083e5af87d44d240d814254ebdb61f5a654","tid":31044,"uid":50329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:50:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>投咩票?講緊咩?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.elections.gov.hk/ecss2016/chi/images/index_16_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Fecss2016%2Fchi%2Fimages%2Findex_16_2.jpg&h=f72df08a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"100c243ba0d2b0dcd82015b07d0fd0d1210a3972","tid":31044,"uid":50329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:52:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>投咩票?講緊咩?</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/2016%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83%E7%95%8C%E5%88%A5%E5%88%86%E7%B5%84%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2016%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%2588%25A5%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%25B5%2584%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589&d=J%2FLuuDr6zUwFy%2B1TchZ5TgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=6d8bec23\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/2016%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83%E7%95%8C%E5%88%A5%E5%88%86%E7%B5%84%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89</a>"},{"pid":"2ecf27e343a0ea601dd45d9aec730dc827bcd45a","tid":31044,"uid":50329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:53:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>投咩票?講緊咩?</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=2_453679_0&amp;category_guid=nextplus&amp;category=magazine\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D2_453679_0%26category_guid%3Dnextplus%26category%3Dmagazine&d=J%2FLuuDr6zUwFy%2B1TchZ5TgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=0f3e9ef7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D2_453679_0%26category_guid%3Dnextplus%26category%3Dmagazine&h=5d182df6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=2_453679_0&amp;category_guid=nextplus&amp;category=magazine</a>"},{"pid":"0a3e551e514cf6cafd65eeb6a7299216150c72b6","tid":31044,"uid":50329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:53:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>投咩票?講緊咩?</blockquote><br />\n到底甚麼是選委？他們又與特首選舉有何關係？&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n選舉委員會共有1200人，分四大界別，每個界別300人。而四大界別之中，又再細分為38個界別分組，例如飲食界、進出口界、會計界、工程界等等。最近備受討論的選委分組選舉，就是讓近25萬名合資格選民，投票選出自己所屬分組的選委，讓他們代表自己投票選特首。不過，在這些分組當中，有300人是自動當選，當中包括中國人民政治協商會議、香港中國企業協會、香港僱主聯合會和漁農界等。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，第二界別（專業界）的分組選舉，是最多非建制派爭取的席位。律師、醫生、護士、會計師、IT人士等紛組成聯盟出戰，參選成為選委候選人，故不少專業人士都有份投票選選委。不過，選舉事務處日前取消了幾名參選人的參選資格，例如有表明反對梁振英連任的「進步工程」的前線工人，被指同業界連繫不足而遭取消資格，中大學生會前會長、「學界同盟2017」的張秀賢亦被指提名無效。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n扣除自動當選的300席、港區人大和立法會議員的103席，以及宗教界自動提名和選出的60個席位，合資格選民可在12月11日的分組選舉中投票，選出超過700人做選委，最終達至1200人的選舉委員會，明年有份在小圈子特首選舉中代表香港市民選出新一任行政長官。"},{"pid":"34335c34d93024a7b792fb17b9f57e0462edb41b","tid":31044,"uid":50329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>投咩票?講緊咩?</blockquote><br />\n投票日將有1,239名候選人競逐25個界別分組／小組共733個席位"},{"pid":"92daa397550ff01dc18a7ffe1539e61b861e341f","tid":31044,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:55:22.000Z","msg":"點知自己有冇資格投票？"},{"pid":"ea6f4c22c18eb121847b5bc7a6bcdc8cbae9e08c","tid":31044,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:56:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21543f96081e7112f17576f2cf068980d1218ecb","tid":31044,"uid":50329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:01:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55b0c63c2d256ab4da2baf65239afaee38b7ad11","tid":31044,"uid":50329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:07:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/cy%E6%A3%84%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB%E5%8D%81%E5%95%8F%E5%8D%81%E7%AD%94/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fcy%25E6%25A3%2584%25E9%2580%25A3%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%2595%258F%25E5%258D%2581%25E7%25AD%2594%2F&d=J%2FLuuDr6zUwFy%2B1TchZ5TgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=f7cb50a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fcy%25E6%25A3%2584%25E9%2580%25A3%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%2595%258F%25E5%258D%2581%25E7%25AD%2594%2F&h=20dc2098\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/cy%E6%A3%84%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB%E5%8D%81%E5%95%8F%E5%8D%81%E7%AD%94/</a><br />\n<br />\nCY棄連任十問十答<br />\n<br />\n林一鳴  2016/12/9 &mdash; 20:04<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問題1︰梁振英宣佈不爭連任，稱要照顧家人，是真的嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我估︰「要照顧家人而不爭連任」的理由，估計連小學生也不會相信吧？你竟然相信？<br />\n<br />\n問題2︰真正原因是甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n我估︰應該是「明明綠燈，轉眼變成紅燈」。如果ABC加反對派超過600票，會很大鑊。<br />\n<br />\n問題3︰今天是甚麼大日子，為甚麼選擇在今天才講？<br />\n<br />\n我估︰今天沒有甚麼特別，但兩天後就是一個大日子，因為有選委會的選舉。原本在當天集中火力喊ABC的泛民&hellip;&hellip;死火了，現在講乜好？講CBA？如果講CBA，人家點解要投你泛民？<br />\n<br />\n問題4︰他不連任了，有機會將樓市辣招取消嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我估︰現在還沒有天黑，請不要發夢。<br />\n<br />\n問題5︰對樓市有影響嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我估︰沒有。就算他不連任，官員暫時只會躲在一旁睇戲，不會跑出來改變重大政策，辣招也會繼續。<br />\n<br />\n問題6︰對股市有影響嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我估︰除了因為一男子因素而得到很多麻煩的那間公司，我看不到其他公司的股價，有甚麼原因會上升或下跌。港股會繼續牛二，繼續上落市。<br />\n<br />\n問題7︰地產股會上升或下跌嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我估︰關乜事？無論他連任與否，地產股都沒有重大的直接影響。<br />\n<br />\n問題8︰梁營股會上升或下跌嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我估︰乜香港有梁營股的嗎？&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n問題9︰未來三到四年私樓供應量，會否可以達到原來說的93,000個目標？<br />\n<br />\n我估︰你竟然相信這個目標，是否太天真，太傻？就算他連任，都肯定不會到數的。<br />\n<br />\n問題10︰「林一鳴的第十個預言」錯了，點算？<br />\n<br />\n我的答案︰今次很特別，估錯後感到有點開心，沒有一點失落的感覺。聽說好似很多人都希望我估錯。"},{"pid":"012afd603e7de37c8e3f4c6a4d2cc8977a04c5a8","tid":31044,"uid":15484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:14:49.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"7c0e66948aa7f8f2b3d1ca9e1522a64d9af6d5f0","tid":31044,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:28:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/cy%E6%A3%84%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB%E5%8D%81%E5%95%8F%E5%8D%81%E7%AD%94/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fcy%25E6%25A3%2584%25E9%2580%25A3%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%2595%258F%25E5%258D%2581%25E7%25AD%2594%2F&d=J%2FLuuDr6zUwFy%2B1TchZ5TgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=f7cb50a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fcy%25E6%25A3%2584%25E9%2580%25A3%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%2595%258F%25E5%258D%2581%25E7%25AD%2594%2F&h=20dc2098\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/cy%E6%A3%84%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB%E5%8D%81%E5%95%8F%E5%8D%81%E7%AD%94/</a><br />\n<br />\n問題6︰對股市有影響嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我估︰除了因為一男子因素而得到很多麻煩的那間公司，我看不到其他公司的股價，有甚麼原因會上升或下跌。<span style=\"color: red;\">港股會繼續牛二</span>，繼續上落市。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542c904ad65c32f610fa61d1289a11fd9b9fe503","tid":31044,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ce17e774f2cfd6fc644907a2a6a0ab14784d03","tid":31044,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T11:31:18.000Z","msg":"樓豬好波"}]}